OL,6,F"So we always want people to come to
OL,7,Fthe beach and have fun while they're
OL,8,Fpaddleboarding," said sam Johns, a
OL,9,Flifeguard at the beach.
OL,11,F"It's pretty similar to driving a car-
OL,12,F you wouldn't go without a seatbelt."
OL,14,FPaddleboarding boomed in the pandemic,
OL,15,Fwith many taking up the sport, but now
OL,16,Fthere are worries that some haven't
OL,17,Flearnt how to do it safely.
