OL,6,FThe number of paddleboarders being
OL,7,Frescued at sea is now six times higher
OL,8,Fthan it was five years ago, last year
OL,9,Falone, lifeboat crews had to launch
OL,10,F155 times to rescue paddleboarders,
OL,11,Fcompared to just 52 in 2019.
OL,13,FMatthew Barker-Smith is a three times
OL,14,Fnational champion paddleboarder and
OL,15,Finstructor in Swansea.
OL,17,F"You see people, using the paddle the
OL,18,Fwrong ay around, standing on the board
OL,19,Fincorrectly." he says.
